80434e29579fd202e34f2900d855","tid":317820,"uid":28507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T17:13:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>上嚟支持下先</blockquote><br />\n多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇心事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有呀<br />\n明明佢自己追我先嘅 只係timing一直都錯<br />\n到而家我覺得ready想追佢但係佢又反而避我<br />\n個感覺好差好難受 本身係好好朋友而家咁驚令朋友都無得做</blockquote><br />\n一直糾纏咗好耐？<br />\n點避法先？ 感情呢啲要慢慢嚟"},{"pid":"0f3b31e0dbfd0b59a0287406ec147646cfe78c74","tid":317820,"uid":127508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T17:17:03.000Z","msg":"冇心事，say 個hi <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec0f2aa5d59646a1bd96ee60eea2031e4e58061c","tid":317820,"uid":83538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T17:17:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>上嚟支持下先</blockquote><br />\n多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇心事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有呀<br />\n明明佢自己追我先嘅 只係timing一直都錯<br />\n到而家我覺得ready想追佢但係佢又反而避我<br />\n個感覺好差好難受 本身係好好朋友而家咁驚令朋友都無得做</blockquote><br />\n一直糾纏咗好耐？<br />\n點避法先？ 感情呢啲要慢慢嚟</blockquote><br />\n其實都兩年<br />\n人前我地係超級好好嘅朋友<br />\n但係之前我地雙方一直有另一半之後我方手<br />\n但係佢借醉表過白<br />\n咁我又唔想帽佢當時男朋友<br />\n後來到我又有新女朋友<br />\n到我分手後我又未放低ex所以唔想無朋友做<br />\n而家終於我想試踏出一步反而佢俾我嘅感覺係開始避我<br />\n行街睇戲食飯我地以前成日做而家佢會唔肯同我做"},{"pid":"19896678d1541327d657c53219df36b78967426d","tid":317820,"uid":67878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T17:17:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d24189e27ee623984da418d8d9deef172ab1bceb","tid":317820,"uid":117297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T17:18:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad60bacee4b31f2e94a0989408cb60d46643a917","tid":317820,"uid":28507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T17:21:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇心事，say 個hi <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你好啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"547b58a56dcc3f0538dfb0b3dc34320350f1b188","tid":317820,"uid":17412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T17:21:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>上嚟支持下先</blockquote><br />\n多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇心事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有呀<br />\n明明佢自己追我先嘅 只係timing一直都錯<br />\n到而家我覺得ready想追佢但係佢又反而避我<br />\n個感覺好差好難受 本身係好好朋友而家咁驚令朋友都無得做</blockquote><br />\n一直糾纏咗好耐？<br />\n點避法先？ 感情呢啲要慢慢嚟</blockquote><br />\n其實都兩年<br />\n人前我地係超級好好嘅朋友<br />\n但係之前我地雙方一直有另一半之後我方手<br />\n但係佢借醉表過白<br />\n咁我又唔想帽佢當時男朋友<br />\n後來到我又有新女朋友<br />\n到我分手後我又未放低ex所以唔想無朋友做<br />\n而家終於我想試踏出一步反而佢俾我嘅感覺係開始避我<br />\n行街睇戲食飯我地以前成日做而家佢會唔肯同我做</blockquote><br />\n同巴情況好相似 明明好似已經變咗啱傾既朋友，突又好冷漠，到我feel到有啲鍾意佢時，佢已經同緊第二個傾得埋咁，若即若離咁，我都唔知點"},{"pid":"4c42c5bc66fc47ff7382cd6aa6f1c130f4588e41","tid":317820,"uid":17412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T17:22:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>上嚟支持下先</blockquote><br />\n多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇心事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有呀<br />\n明明佢自己追我先嘅 只係timing一直都錯<br />\n到而家我覺得ready想追佢但係佢又反而避我<br />\n個感覺好差好難受 本身係好好朋友而家咁驚令朋友都無得做</blockquote><br />\n一直糾纏咗好耐？<br />\n點避法先？ 感情呢啲要慢慢嚟</blockquote><br />\n其實都兩年<br />\n人前我地係超級好好嘅朋友<br />\n但係之前我地雙方一